race.comment: TERESITA (1) is having her first look at this circuit. Strong winner last time by 2.5 lengths at Q Parklands in a Grade 4/5 in one of the quickest times on the program (29.81). Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Looks to have an edge on most of these. HONK HONK (2) has been out of the placings at her last two outings but shapes well for this if she can recapture her powerful win a few runs back, getting around Gosford over 515m in 29.41. Has the ability and can find winning form again. SAMMY ETHAN (8) hit the ground running to win over the 520m at this track two runs back then prominent throughout when finishing third at Dubbo last start. Form from his last run is proving strong. Must be included in calculations. CANYA SAPPHIRE (3) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish here at this distance.
